{"id": 2740, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有哪些个人数据，现在已经放弃整理了？", "description": "我们所产生的海量数据已经快要超过自己能够处理的范畴，你发愁吗？（题图来自：iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 1828, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190115115745j9zx0sPAkD315ZBW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 325120, "content": "手机通讯录里的人。电话太多，分类太少，很多人还不认识了，都需要重新备注。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570214}, {"id": 325121, "content": "弃用app的注册账号，懒得注销了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059941}, {"id": 325634, "content": "图库和各类app的账号", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451953}, {"id": 325123, "content": "成绩单啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 325125, "content": "微博收藏，好多还没看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 325126, "content": "心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427396}, {"id": 325127, "content": "自从生了娃，照片已经来不及导进电脑了，各种云上传，要是未来哪天什么云☁️退出历史舞台，我的照片视频都不知何处安放。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567093}, {"id": 325128, "content": "各类app以及网站的账号密码绑定手机，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927713}, {"id": 325129, "content": "收藏的文章和视频", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428228}, {"id": 325130, "content": "理想的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570319}, {"id": 325386, "content": "各种账号密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570998}, {"id": 325388, "content": "手机里的图片，尤其是截图；百度云里的各种资源；移动硬盘里的影视剧；微信里的收藏；浏览器的书签、收藏夹；手机备忘录……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571022}, {"id": 325134, "content": "电子设备里，网上的各类资料", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447988}, {"id": 325136, "content": "无论什么数据每隔一段时间都会整理，觉得这样才有安全感哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}, {"id": 325139, "content": "电脑桌面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737041}, {"id": 326678, "content": "各种电脑复习文件", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1575996}, {"id": 325914, "content": "井井有条，不会有整理不了的情况存在，会把它们扼杀在出生的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397575}, {"id": 326694, "content": "大姨妈啥时候来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578708}, {"id": 322860, "content": "手机里各种截图啥的，以前用完了还删，现在都随它去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 418, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322861, "content": "照片没空整理，看看 memory 自动生成的小短片就算回顾了", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322863, "content": "聊天记录，手机容量越买越大，也不删也不筛了，直接全部搬迁", "image": null, "praise_count": 249, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 329776, "content": "聊天记录，短信，不少不舒服，喜欢干干净净的页面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 325170, "content": "微博里收藏的小贴士", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435693}, {"id": 325429, "content": "QQ访客", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514606}, {"id": 325941, "content": "表情包", "image": "img/option/option/20190202193143jbuH9zdnYMfZtSVF", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573897}, {"id": 325178, "content": "各种验证码短信还有每日运营商发的流量套餐详细使用情况都懒得删了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570542}, {"id": 325190, "content": "朋友圈杂乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570569}, {"id": 325448, "content": "手机里照片视频截图……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033420}, {"id": 328009, "content": "微信标签🏷️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584712}, {"id": 325451, "content": "我的网易云音乐歌单…一千五百多首了…力不从心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568010}, {"id": 326995, "content": "目前还没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563928}, {"id": 325221, "content": "照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737671}, {"id": 325231, "content": "大学里，聊的热火朝天的那些人，通讯录、微信聊天、图片截图、合照，现在毕业了，基本也不联系，但也不删，他们是我大学的青春，只为以后同学聚会，不会尴尬的不认识这是我曾经认识的谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537948}, {"id": 325240, "content": "全部个人数据", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1569874}, {"id": 325512, "content": "各种收藏夹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497432}, {"id": 325773, "content": "照片，截图", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523082}, {"id": 331410, "content": "亲情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832221}, {"id": 325013, "content": "当然是学校发的卷子和通知🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568370}, {"id": 325014, "content": "百度云里自动上传的各种照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 326550, "content": "QQ三四年没碰过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577566}, {"id": 325015, "content": "强迫症表示 必须整理", "image": null, "praise_count": 206, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438442}, {"id": 325528, "content": "公司资料，特别多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571840}, {"id": 325018, "content": "qq好友分组 \n微信标签", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412338}, {"id": 325787, "content": "2016年记帐记了半年 很详细 主要是没有琐碎的花销 然后发现根本没用…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "p